{"tid":749354,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"施治驚人新樣貌令球迷驚呼：呢個夏天做左乜野？","createTime":"2018-07-20T03:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T04:33:39.000Z","uid":4661,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c4be0cd29bd298456b03f7df262a1fa240af8cf7","tid":749354,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/07/20/c/c8c596186772724a2e301b19dc0c7382.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2Fc%2Fc8c596186772724a2e301b19dc0c7382.jpg&h=6ea05f30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴守門員彼特-施治現身訓練場，兵工廠球迷們一看捷克人的身形，不禁驚訝的喊出了聲：施治怎麼了？<br />\n　　36歲的施治突然之間變得強壯了許多，他上身膨脹，肌肉發達，和以往的形象截然不同。施治的「新身體」，讓槍迷們紛紛「抽水」，看來他這個夏天沒少去健身房啊。<br />\n　　在Twitter上，有球迷說：「看來施治這個夏天一直住在健身房了」，有人戲稱他為「彼特-阿諾舒華辛力加」，還有人調侃：「施治看起來像綠巨人！」<br />\n　　此前有傳聞稱，車路士想把施治買回史坦福橋，但施治的經理人克拉爾在ESPN的節目中予以了否認。「每一個轉會窗口期間，關於施治都會有很多傳聞，因為他是英超中的優秀球員。不過，他現在完全專注於阿仙奴的新賽季。」"},{"pid":"3f2ef6bce11675e6c5dbdc637506aace9fb3380a","tid":749354,"uid":117187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:23:19.000Z","msg":"龍門練咁大隻會唔會影響反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b614aa758cec215e86dc08ec10f2c18c75467bb1","tid":749354,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:36:06.000Z","msg":"肥到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41bce52e68d5ac68db08ccb7df4234186d455df","tid":749354,"uid":57035,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T03:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/P9lxBQZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FP9lxBQZ.jpg&h=66fa93e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c2daf809